{"tid":554930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【睇人跳樓變自己跳樓】「花生男」墜樓亡 輕生女嚇得爬回陽台","createTime":"2018-02-09T03:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T09:20:26.000Z","uid":49208,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b138d7a7eed3b9cf4ff47cceb92c139469657c39","tid":554930,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:32:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180207/_2018020721145417156.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180207%2F_2018020721145417156.jpg&h=7d94280b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四川成都一名女子爬上8樓外的橫樑上，雙腳懸空危坐，群眾急忙報警，豈料就在救護人員到場救援的一刻，對面大樓一名看熱鬧的男子不慎從高處墜下慘死，讓原本企圖輕生的女子急忙爬回大樓裡。<br />\n<br />\n成都一名穿著粉紅色上衣的年輕女子，昨日 (6日) 孤身爬上大樓8樓的橫樑，她雙腳懸空跨坐在橫樑上，情況非常危險，陽台內的群眾急忙與她說話，試圖讓她轉移注意力，其他人則報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n救護人員隨後趕到，豈料大樓對面的9樓，一名男子突然從高處墜下，跌在停放在地面的一輛汽車上，當場慘死。據目擊者表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">這名墜樓男子當時在現場「看熱鬧」，更不顧自身安危爬上陽台，結果一個不小心就失足墜下，但他原本沒有輕生的念頭。<br />\n</span><br />\n而原本打算輕生的女子，目睹男子墜樓慘死後，嚇得立刻放棄，隨著救護人員爬回大樓陽台內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d872782c0e9908bc40594274f6577637e51e385","tid":554930,"uid":82098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">THIS</span></span>"},{"pid":"2b411e492542fa994940eb426537c9e46fea438c","tid":554930,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d872782c0e9908bc40594274f6577637e51e385","tid":554930,"uid":82098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T03:34:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">THIS</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T04:13:15.000Z","msg":"幾日比人回左幾廿次"},{"pid":"c1c034884c2ee25a62be01e0e8ddb0d13ae77746","tid":554930,"uid":54517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"娘子,快D出黎食花生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">呀</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">呀</span>"},{"pid":"219a53da083a882e6feb940ac7392c92c97efed0","tid":554930,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"佢唔係慘死係抵死囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f0963191053fdcdc489397ae39d0821aa00a71","tid":554930,"uid":143572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T09:20:26.000Z","msg":"用生命去拯救生命,好偉大。"}]}